Pagedown CVs

Ulrik Lyngs

05/04/2019

This repository has three different versions of my resume (NOTE: 1 and 2 does not work in the Safari browser):

  1. Short, 2-page professional resume
  2. Paged full resume
  3. Ordinary scrolling HTML resume

The resums pull in different subsets of cv entries that live in two separate Excel files on my machine (one for publications, one for all other cv entries).

The paged resums are made with pagedown.
